Reverend Father '''Paul Bovier-Lapierre''' (1873&ndash;1950) was a [[France|French]] [[Jesuit]] [[Archaeology|archaeologist]], notable for his work on [[prehistory]] in [[Egypt]] and surveys in southern [[Lebanon]].<ref name="Bovier-LapierreGauthier1932">{{cite book|author1=Paul Bovier-Lapierre|author2=H. Gauthier|author3=P. Jouguet|title=Egypte Préhistorique: pharaonique et gréco romaine|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xbxFGwAACAAJ|accessdate=22 July 2011|year=1932|publisher=Institut français d'archéologie orientale}}</ref>

