'''''The Stepmother's Tragedy''''' is a [[Play (theatre)|play]] written by [[Henry Chettle]] and [[Thomas Dekker (poet)|Thomas Dekker]]. It is mentioned in [[Philip Henslowe]]'s diary in August 1599. No extant copies of the play are known.

